parameters: The survivors are on floor 77. They give Chambers Key
after boss fight after entering corpse room on 78.
To enter corpse room, you need the Twisting Cutters
Corpse room nets you the laboratory key, which you
won't need until you enter the labs floor 58 in order
Floor 55 has the Council Key, that lets you obtain the
Archmage's Monocle. It's right next to the stairs, but
you can't go any further or you get hit by the evil.
Finally, the Focus Key is needed to enter the power
terminal room on floor 74, to turn on the elevator
